body.name: Tieplis Frying Pans Nonstick Skillet, 3 Piece Nonstick Frying Pan with 8"/9.5"/11" 3 Sizes Pan, Stay Cool Handle, Easy Clean Effect Coating, PFOA FREE, Induction & Dishwasher Safe
deliveryMessages: FREE delivery Tuesday, February 20 on orders shipped by Amazon over $35
features: 【SET OF THREE NON STICK FRYING PANS】 The processional 3-piece nonstick pan set includes three versatile sizes induction pan perfect for any task, Small (8inch / 20cm diameter), Medium (9.5inch / 24cm diameter) and Large (11inch / 28cm diameter).

【ALUMINUM BODY FOR FAST, EVEN HEAT】The cooking pans are made with a sturdy 5-player aluminum body for fast, incredibly even heat distribution. From omelet to fried bacon to stir-frys - this non stick pans set can handle it all, our non stick frying pans are strong enough to last a lifetime.

【INCREDIBLE NON-STICK PERFORMANCE】Each pan features a nonstick coating for outstanding strength and durability. Non-Stick interior and exterior that provides outstanding performance and easy hand wash clean. This non stick frying pan is recommended for use with wooden, silicone or nylon utensils to avoid damaging the non stick coating.

【SAFE, HEALTHY AND CONVENIENT】Slippery toxin-free nonstick coating made without potentially toxic materials like PFAS (including PTFEs and PFOAs), lead and cadmium. You can cook healthier because little to no oil is needed, and because nothing sticks to the skillet, cleaning is an absolute breeze!
【WORKS ON ALL STOVES】This pans set nonstick is compatible with all cooktops, including induction, electric, ceramic, halogen, gas and glass, this induction pan is also dishwasher safe.
【HEAT RESISTANT HANDLES】Featuring a soft-touch Bakelite handle, which will withstand high temperatures, the nonstick pan is strong and durable to withstand the demands of a busy kitchen.

【12-MONTH WARRANTY】About this pan, the exterior coating is not entirely black. It is actually designed a red looking. These non stick frying pans is one year warranty. If you have any questions, please feel free to contact us.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 28, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Definitely non stick!
reviews.reviewText: This 3 pack of different sized frying pans are pretty good. The non-stick, surface has seem to work well for the few times I've used the small pan when I'm frying up eggs in the morning. The first day I use just a little bit of butter as that's what I normally do and on the second day I didn't use any and I waited for the egg to get crispy and then it was actually very easy to hand flip within the pan. So I'd say the non-stick surfaces pretty good.The one photo shows the bottom of the pans that look to be great for induction heat as well as any other type of stove top which the product description say it's good for gas or propane, electric, induction and one other which I can't remember off top of head.I wasn't sure about the wooden handle when we place the order and once I got it I wasn't too keen on it but the handle is very smooth easy to hold and actually feels very lightweight compared to other pans of the same size.The only issue I have, and why I gave it a four-star, is because the handles don't feel super secure to the actual pan and upon first touching it I almost thought it was going to fall off but it didn't. I attempted to turn the handle and see if anything happened which it did not, so it looks like these handles are secured to the pan nicely but I still feel it's just a slight little movement when I'm holding the pan in my hand.The three different sizes are great for everyday household use if you need to quickly fry an egg saute some onions or mushrooms and or saute or fry up something in the larger pan.
